0 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-18 brz-fs-xs-im-18 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> Mental Health is a growing area of focus as wellness for employees. Stress, burn-out, anxiety are the next frontier to consciously lookout for and create avenues for mental wellbeing. These issues at times get more layered for LGBTI employees, with their experiences of social anxiety, bullying, harassment at home/school/work etc.</span></p><p class="brz-ff-lato brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-18 brz-fs-xs-im-18 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6"><br></p><p class="brz-text-xs-justify brz-ff-lato brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-18 brz-fs-xs-im-18 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> Pride Circle in collaboration with WYSA brings this fabulous program to get better employee engagement and identify early signals to enable a culture of inclusion and wellness for all employees. Providing a safe, non-judgements, anonymous way to engage on the topic of LGBTI inclusion & mental wellness, we are bringing all employees to the table, to be heard and enabled.</span></p><p class="brz-ff-lato brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-18 brz-fs-xs-im-18 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6"><br></p><p class="brz-text-xs-justify brz-tp-paragraph brz-ff-lato brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-17 brz-fs-sm-im-18 brz-fs-xs-im-18 brz-lh-lg-1_5 brz-lh-sm-im-1_6 brz-lh-xs-im-1_6"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> Give the widget a go, and as you fall in love with it, download the app </span><a href="https://app.wysa.io/pridecircle" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(35, 157, 219);" class="link--external" data-brz-link-type="external">here</a><a href="https://app.wysa.io/pridecircle" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" class="link--external" data-brz-link-type="external">.</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id class="brz-css-brytp brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-nckco"><div class="brz-embed-code brz-css-jvbvx" data-custom-id="qamsypotqauaufsrxdwweudqhmyyurmuegeb"><div class="brz-embed-content"><div class><iframe id="wysa_widget" src="https://web.wysa.io/?mode=embed&key=55ac-8d33-8b14-7115-9a3638719-a9" height="720" width="480" style="border: 1px solid #3A8692; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></div></div></div><div id class="brz-css-brytp brz-wrapper"><div class="brz-d-xs-flex brz-css-nckco"><div class="brz-rich-text brz-css-sxdfd" data-custom-id="hicvasskhtamoyydlgpopxuqimlqyniocxpk"><p class="brz-text-lg-center brz-ff-noto_serif brz-ft-google brz-fw-lg-400 brz-fw-sm-im-400 brz-fw-xs-im-400 brz-fs-lg-13 brz-fs-sm-im-12 brz-fs-xs-im-12 brz-lh-lg-1_7 brz-lh-sm-im-1_4 brz-lh-xs-im-1_4 brz-ls-lg-0_5 brz-ls-sm-im-1 brz-ls-xs-im-1"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> Copyright © 2020 Pride Circle. All Rights Reserved</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section></div> <script class="brz-script brz-script-polyfill" src="https://www.thepridecircle.com/site/templates/assets/b3787f9f967b597785615e5c373cd668.js"></script><script class="brz-script brz-script-preview" src="https://www.thepridecircle.com/site/templates/assets/9f7d79e86a1549251ca3199d557752d4.js"></script><script class="brz-script brz-script-preview-pro" src="https://www.thepridecircle.com/site/templates/assets/8d895f21903ca784b4706b4e6ff4d36e.js"></script><script class="brz-script brz-script-emit">     jQuery(document).ready(function() {         window.Brizy.emit("init.dom", jQuery(document.body));     }); </script></body></html>